  <original-body>Activerecord 2.1.0 uses the DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS statement which is only supported by PostgreSQL versions &gt;= 8.2. Since there are quite a few older PG installations in use it might be a good idea to try and be backwards compatible here. (I don't know if there are any other compatibility issues that might be more difficult to resolve though)</original-body>
